@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}


@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<section class="container py-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted">Your privacy is important to us. This page describes how we collect, use, and protect your data when using the InfraIT Solution portal.</p>

            <hr class="my-4">

            <h3 class="h4 mt-4">1. Data Collection</h3>
            <p>We collect information that you provide directly to us, such as:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Account information (Name, Email, Job Title) provided during registration.</li>
                <li>Technical data (Logs, IP addresses, browser type) collected automatically to ensure system security and stability.</li>
                <li>Ticket records and communication history related to infrastructure incidents.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h4 mt-4">2. Purpose of Processing</h3>
            <p>The data is used exclusively to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Provide and manage your access to the ITSM portal.</li>
                <li>Process and resolve technical incidents (Tickets).</li>
                <li>Monitor system performance and prevent unauthorized access or abuse.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="h4 mt-4">3. Data Retention</h3>
            <p>Account and incident data are retained only as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which they were collected, or to comply with legal and professional requirements.</p>

            <h3 class="h4 mt-4">4. Your Rights</h3>
            <p>You have the right to access, rectify, or request the deletion of your personal data. To exercise these rights, please contact the system administrator or email <a href="mailto:support@infraitsolution.com">support@infraitsolution.com</a>.</p>

            <h3 class="h4 mt-4">5. Third-Party Services</h3>
            <p>We do not sell your data. We may share information with trusted service providers (e.g., email notification services) strictly to support operations, under confidentiality agreements.</p>

            <h3 class="h4 mt-4">6. Security</h3>
            <p>We implement industry-standard security measures (SSL/TLS encryption) to protect your data from unauthorized access or disclosure.</p>

            <div class="mt-5 p-3 bg-light border rounded">
                <p class="mb-0 text-muted small">Last updated: June 20, 2026</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
